de.interactive_instruments.etf.testdriver

Interface TestTaskResultPersistor


  • public interface TestTaskResultPersistor
    The TestTaskResultPersistor provides a abstract layer for persisting the results of a Test Task. There are three ways to persist a result: - collect results with a TestResultCollector object - save a file that already is in the ETF Test Task result XML format - Persist a Test Task result object
